headline: Who is Giuliani hoping to get dirt on in a trip to Ukraine?
description: One of the president’s lawyers is heading overseas to chat with a familiar foreign government. His mission is “not meddling in an election, we’re meddling in an investigation.” Former Congresswoman Jane Harman joins Stephanie Ruhle to discuss where Rudy Giulani is going and who he is hoping to get dirt on.
creator: MSNBC.com
